reenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002157, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, the Lord, (this is) the month of Ramazan, in it, Thou revealed the Holy Qur’an, and in it made obligatory “fasting” upon Thy servants, send blessings on Muhammad and on the children of Muhammad, and provide us with the means to go to Thy Sacred House for “Hajj” this year and every year; and in this month forgive my grave sins, verily, other than Thee, no one can liberate (me) from its consequences, O Beneficent O Omniscient.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khudaaya! Ay Mahe Ramazan ke maalik, jisne Qur’an ko utaara hai, aur apne bando’n par roza waajib kiya hai. Mohammed (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Mohammed (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma aur hamein Hajje Baytullah ki taufiq ataa farma, isi saal aur har saal, hamare azeem gunaho’n ko maaf kar de, keh aise gunaho’n ko Tere alaawa koi maaf nahi kar sakta, ay Khudaaye Rehmaan, ay Khudaaye Alaam.", "Urdu": "اے اللہ! اے ماہ رمضان کے پروردگار کہ جس میں تو نے قرآن کریم نازل فرمایا اور اپنے بندوں پر اس ماہ میں روزے رکھنا فرض کیے محمدؐ و آل محمدؐ پر رحمت نازل فرما اور مجھے اسی سال اپنے بیت الحرام (کعبہ) کا حج نصیب فرما اور آئندہ سالوں میں بھی اور میرے اب تک کے تمام گناہان کبیرہ معاف کر دے کیوں کہ سوائے تیرے انہیں کوئی معاف نہیں کرسکتا اے زیادہ رحم والے اے زیادہ علم والے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA RABBA SHAHRE RAMAZAA-NAL LAZEE ANZAL-TA FEE-HIL QURAANA, WAF-TARAZ-TA A’LAA E’BAADE-KA FEE-HIL QURAANA, WAF-TARAZ-TA A’LAA E’BAADE-KA FEE-HIS SEYAAMA. SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WAR-ZUQNEE HAJJA BAIYTE-KAL HARAANE, FEE AA’MEE HAAZAA WA FEE KULLE AA’MIN, WAGH-FIR LEE TILKAZ ZONOO-BAL E’ZAAMA FA-INNA-HU LAA YAGH-FERO-HAA GHAIRO-KA YAA RAHMAA-NO YAA A’LLAAM.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ رَبَّ شَہْرِ رَمَضَانَ الَّذِیْ اَنْزَلْتَ فِیْہِ الْقُرْاٰنَ، وَافْتَرَضْتَ عَلٰی عِبَادِکَ فِیْہِ الْقُرْاٰنَ، وَافْتَرَضْتَ عَلٰی عِبَادِکَ فِیْہِ الصِّیَامَ، صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَارْزُقْنِیْ حَجَّ بَیْتِکَ الْحَرَامِ، فِیْ عَامِیْ ہٰذَا وَفِیْ کُلِّ عَامٍ، وَاغْفِرْلِیْ تِلْکَ الذُّنُوْبَ الْعِظَامَ، فَاِنَّہٗ لَا یَغْفِرُہَا غَیْرُکَ یَارَحْمٰنُ یَاعَلَّامُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "Ar